<li id="cite_note-BushDialogue-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-8"><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-9"><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-10"><sup><i><b>k</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-11"><sup><i><b>l</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BushDialogue_16-12"><sup><i><b>m</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBush1973" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Lester_E._Bush_Jr." title="Lester E. Bush Jr.">Bush, Lester E.</a> (1973). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/sbi/articles/Dialogue_V08N01_13.pdf">"Mormonism's Negro Doctrine: An Historical Overview"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue</a></i>. <b>8</b> (1). <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue&amp;rft.atitle=Mormonism%27s+Negro+Doctrine%3A+An+Historical+Overview&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.aulast=Bush&amp;r