</li>
<li id="cite_note-Jackson-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Jackson_17-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Jackson_17-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Jackson_17-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFJackson" class="citation book cs1">Jackson, W. Kesler. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=4EwCdjQ7uvoC"><i>Elijah Abel: The Life and Times of a Black Priesthood Holder</i></a>. Cedar Fort. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781462103560" title="Special:BookSources/9781462103560"><bdi>9781462103560</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Elijah+Abel%3A+The+Life+and+Times+of+a+Black+Priesthood+Holder&amp;rft.pub=Cedar+Fort&amp;rft.isbn=9781462103560&amp;rft.aulast=Jackson&amp;rft.aufirst=W.+Kesler&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D4EwCdjQ7uvoC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
