<li id="cite_note-Odyssey-36"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Odyssey_36-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Odyssey_36-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHarris2022" class="citation journal cs1">Harris, Matthew L. (Fall 2022). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/articles/joseph-fielding-smiths-evolving-views-on-race-the-odyssey-of-a-mormon-apostle-president/#pdf-wrap">"Joseph Fielding Smith's Evolving Views on Race: The Odyssey of a Mormon Apostle-President"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue</a></i>. <b>55</b> (3). <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>: 1–41. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.5406%2F15549399.55.3.01">10.5406/15549399.55.3.01</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:253368389">253368389</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue&amp;rft.atitle=Joseph+Fielding+Smith%27s+Evolving+Views+on+Race%3A+The+Odyssey+of+a+Mormon+Apostle-President&amp;rft.ssn=fall&amp;rft.volume=55&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=1-41&amp;rft.date=2022&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.5406%2F15549399.55.3.01&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A253368389%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Harris&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew+L.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dialoguejournal.com%2Fartic