<li id="cite_note-Harris2020-112"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2020_112-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2020_112-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHarrisBringhurst2020" class="citation book cs1">Harris, Matthew L.; <a href="/wiki/Newell_G._Bringhurst" title="Newell G. Bringhurst">Bringhurst, Newell G.</a> (2020). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=S6qTzQEACAAJ&amp;pg=PA247">"Whiteness Theology and the Evolution of Mormon Racial Teachings"</a>. <i>The LDS Gospel Topics Series: A Scholarly Engagement</i>. <a href="/wiki/Signature_Books" title="Signature Books">Signature Books</a>. pp.&#160;247–280. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-56085-287-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-56085-287-2"><bdi>978-1-56085-287-2</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Whiteness+Theology+and+the+Evolution+of+Mormon+Racial+Teachings&amp;rft.btitle=The+LDS+Gospel+Topics+Series%3A+A+Scholarly+Engagement&amp;rft.pages=247-280&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=2020&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-56085-287-2&amp;rft.aulast=Harris&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew+L.&amp;rft.au=Bringhurst%2C+Newell+G.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DS6qTzQEACAAJ%26pg%3DPA247&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
