<li id="cite_note-Mormonism_and_Secular_Attitudes_toward_Negroes-130"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Mormonism_and_Secular_Attitudes_toward_Negroes_130-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMauss1966" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Armand_L._Mauss" class="mw-redirect" title="Armand L. Mauss">Mauss, Armand L.</a> (October 1966). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/1388243">"Mormonism and Secular Attitudes toward Negroes"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Sociological_Perspectives" title="Sociological Perspectives">The Pacific Sociological Review</a></i>. <b>9</b> (2). <a href="/wiki/Pacific_Sociological_Association" title="Pacific Sociological Association">Pacific Sociological Association</a>: 91–99. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F1388243">10.2307/1388243</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/1388243">1388243</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:158067784">158067784</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Pacific+Sociological+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Mormonism+and+Secular+Attitudes+toward+Negroes&amp;rft.volume=9&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=91-99&amp;rft.date=1966-10&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A158067784%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F1388243%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F1388243&amp;rft.aulast=Mauss&amp;rft.aufirst=Armand+L.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F1388243&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
