<li id="cite_note-Forced-134"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Forced_134-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Forced_134-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGaffey2017" class="citation magazine cs1">Gaffey, Connor (August 17, 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.newsweek.com/charlottesville-mormons-white-supremacists-651747">"How a Charlottesville Speaker Forced the Mormon Church to Condemn 'Sinful' White Supremacists"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Newsweek" title="Newsweek">Newsweek</a></i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Newsweek&amp;rft.atitle=How+a+Charlottesville+Speaker+Forced+the+Mormon+Church+to+Condemn+%27Sinful%27+White+Supremacists&amp;rft.date=2017-08-17&amp;rft.aulast=Gaffey&amp;rft.aufirst=Connor&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fcharlottesville-mormons-white-supremacists-651747&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
