<li id="cite_note-Graham2017-135"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Graham2017_135-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Graham2017_135-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGraham2017" class="citation magazine cs1">Graham, Ruth (August 18, 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.slate.com/blogs/xx_factor/2017/08/18/the_mormon_church_condemned_white_supremacists_and_this_mormon_white_supremacist.html">"The Mormon Church Condemned White Supremacists, and This Mormon White Supremacist Mom Is Very Mad About It"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Slate_(magazine)" title="Slate (magazine)">Slate</a></i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">April 17,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Slate&amp;rft.atitle=The+Mormon+Church+Condemned+White+Supremacists%2C+and+This+Mormon+White+Supremacist+Mom+Is+Very+Mad+About+It&amp;rft.date=2017-08-18&amp;rft.aulast=Graham&amp;rft.aufirst=Ruth&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slate.com%2Fblogs%2Fxx_factor%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2Fthe_mormon_church_condemned_white_supremacists_and_this_mormon_white_supremacist.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
