<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBush1973" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Lester_E._Bush_Jr." title="Lester E. Bush Jr.">Bush, Lester E. Jr.</a> (Spring 1973). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/sbi/articles/Dialogue_V08N01_13.pdf">"Mormonism's Negro Doctrine: An Historical Overview"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought</a></i>. <b>8</b> (1). <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>: 11–68. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F45227533">10.2307/45227533</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/45227533">45227533</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">April 17,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue%3A+A+Journal+of+Mormon+Thought&amp;rft.atitle=Mormonism%27s+Negro+Doctrine%3A+An+Historical+Overview&amp;rft.ssn=spring&amp;rft.volume=8&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=11-68&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F45227533&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F45227533%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.aulast=Bush&amp;rft.aufirst=Lester+E.+Jr.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dialoguejournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsbi%2Farticles%2FDialogue_V08N01_13.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></li></ul>
</div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Black_people_and_Mormonism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.blacklds.org/">BlackLDS.org</a> – Independent (not church-owned or operated) site maintained by some church members.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ldsgenesisgroup.org/">Genesis Group</a> – Church-affiliated organization for serving needs of Black Latter-day Saints.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/topics/race-and-the-priesthood?lang=eng">Race and the Priesthood</a> – 2013 statement by the LDS Church renouncing previous teachings and stating the Church's current stances.</li></ul>
